Privacy Policy

Welcome to [Night Owl] discord BOT. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose 
information about users of our Discord bot ("the Bot").

Information We Collect:

User Data:
User ID: We collect your Discord User ID to provide personalized services and functionalities within the Bot.
Username and Discriminator: We collect your Discord username and discriminator to identify you within the Bot.

Messages:
Commands and Interactions: We log commands and interactions you perform with the Bot to ensure proper functionality and improve the user experience.
Direct Messages: We may log direct messages sent to the Bot for support purposes or to enhance user experience.

Guild Data
Guild ID: We collect the Guild ID where the Bot is used to provide server-specific features and settings.
Guild Name: We collect the Guild name to identify the server where the Bot is active.
How We Use Your Information
Providing Services: To operate and maintain the Bot, including processing commands and interactions.
Improving Services: To analyze usage patterns and improve the functionality and performance of the Bot.
Support: To provide customer support and respond to inquiries.
Compliance: To comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms of service.
Information Sharing and Disclosure
Third-Party Services: We may share your data with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the Bot, such as hosting services.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.

Data Retention:
We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including any legal, accounting, or reporting requirements.

Security:
We take reasonable measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or method of 
electronic storage is 100% secure.

Your Rights:
Access: You have the right to access the personal data we hold about you.
Correction: You have the right to request correction of any inaccurate personal data.
Deletion: You have the right to request deletion of your personal data, subject to certain legal obligations.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Effective Date" at
the top.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us on:
